      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <p class="card-label">Backend</p>
      <p class="card-value">
        Node.js, PHP, REST APIs, GraphQL, MySQL, PostgreSQL, SQLite, Qdrant Vector DB, Headless CMS,
        Serverless
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <p class="card-label">AI / LLM</p>
      <p class="card-value">OpenAI API, Anthropic Claude, Google Gemini, RAG, Semantic Search</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <p class="card-label">Architecture</p>
      <p class="card-value">SSG, SSR, ISR, Component Design Systems, State Management</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2>About This Blog</h2>
